        </div>
        <p class="logo-text">
            In the Second Year Pre-K Program, four year olds will have the opportunity to learn to read, write,
            and complete all the necessary skills to ensure an easier transition to kindergarten.
            Preparing them well to meet the growing requirements of elementary school.
            This program will help children learn letters of the alphabet, phonics, beginning number concepts,
            left and right tracking, patterning, sequencing, and reading readiness. Activities, music, movement,
            and crafts are a part of a total learning experience.
        </p>
